Bas de Witte (proposed)
- Make PropertyValueInjector thread safe and extendable (e.g. singleton)
- No longer use the resources annotated at field level for other fields       
- Add setting to optionally throw exception on missing resource
- Add support for loading the properties from a HOME_VAR defined location
- Perhaps add integration with commons configuration2       

Martin Todorov
- Add annotation support on the getter method level.
- Add proper logging.

- Add support for monitoring for property file changes and automatic reloading.
- Add support for forcing a reload of the properties.
- Add support for loading the properties from a database.
- Add support for forcing a reload of the properties from the database.
